response.overview: Children are left at grandma's house without their smartphones. Real life seems rather boring until they find instructions for the Kratt - a magical creature who will do whatever its master says. All they have to do now, is to buy a soul from the devil.
response.tagline: The road to hell is paved with good intentions
response.title: Kratt
